# HexAstral iOS App (hexastral-app) Development Rules

**Loaded automatically when working under `apps/hexastral-app/`. Overrides root rules.**

---

## 1. Quick Facts

| Dimension | Value |
|-----------|-------|
| **App** | HexAstral |
| **Bundle ID** | com.zhop.hexastral |
| **Framework** | Expo 54 + React 19 + React Native 0.81 |
| **Router** | Expo Router 6 (`app/` file-based) |
| **Styling** | NativeWind 4.1 + Tailwind v3 |
| **State** | React Query + MMKV |
| **Design** | Ink Brutalism |

---

## 2. Forbidden Patterns ❌

| Forbidden | Why | Alternative |
|-----------|-----|-------------|
| `bun add expo-*` | SDK version mismatch | `npx expo install expo-*` |
| Hardcoded hex colors | Breaks theme switching | `ios.*` palette or semantic tokens |
| `useState` + `useEffect` for async | Race conditions, leaks | `useQuery` / `useMutation` |
| Decorative Lucide icons | AI-generated look, bad aesthetics | Only functional icons (state, nav) |
| `as Type` assertions | Loses type safety | Zod parse + type guards |
| Empty `catch {}` | Swallows errors | Log or handle explicitly |
| `any` type | 100% type loss | `unknown` + type guards |

---

## 3. Route Architecture (Expo Router)

```
app/
├── _layout.tsx           # Root Stack
├── index.tsx             # Tab entry
├── (tabs)/               # Bottom navigator (persistent)
│   ├── explore.tsx       # Discover
│   ├── bonds.tsx         # Relationships
│   ├── readings.tsx      # History
│   ├── commerce.tsx      # Shop
│   └── settings.tsx      # Settings
├── (auth)/               # Modal: login
├── (birth)/              # Modal: birth info
├── (reading)/[id]        # Modal: detail
├── detail/[id]           # Deep link handler
└── _not-found.tsx        # 404
```

**Navigation**:
```typescript
// ✅ Push modal
router.push({ pathname: '/(reading)/[id]', params: { id: readingId } })

// ✅ Tab switch
router.push('/(tabs)/commerce')

// ❌ Ambiguous — use path prefix
router.push('/reading/123')
```

---

## 4. Styling (Ink Brutalism)

### Theme Palette

```typescript
import { useTheme } from '@/lib/theme'

const { colors, isDark } = useTheme()

// Build iOS palette
const ios = {
  bg:        isDark ? '#09090B' : '#FAFAFA',
  card:      isDark ? '#18181B' : '#FFFFFF',
  separator: isDark ? '#27272A' : '#E4E4E7',
  text:      isDark ? '#FAFAFA' : '#09090B',
  tint:      colors.primary,
  accent:    colors.accent,    // Ink Gold / Ink Brown
}
```

### Forbidden Patterns

```typescript
// ❌ Rainbow borders
<View style={{ borderLeftWidth: 3, borderLeftColor: colors.wuxingFire }} />

// ❌ Rounded, colorful cards
<View style={{ borderRadius: 12, backgroundColor: '#FFE5CC' }} />

// ✅ Flat card
<View style={{ borderWidth: 0.5, borderColor: ios.separator, borderRadius: 0 }} />
```

### Icon Rules

```typescript
// ✅ Functional
<Check size={20} color={ios.accent} />          // state
<ChevronRight size={16} color={ios.secondary} /> // navigation

// ❌ Decorative — no
<Heart size={24} color={ios.tint} />   // on a list item? No.

// Exception: category header may have a small icon
<View style={styles.headerRow}>
  <Heart size={16} color={ios.secondary} />
  <Text>Bonds</Text>
</View>
```

---

## 5. Data Fetching (React Query + MMKV)

```typescript
import { useQuery, useMutation } from '@tanstack/react-query'
import { storage } from '@/lib/storage'

// ✅ Query
const { data, isLoading } = useQuery({
  queryKey: ['readings', userId],
  queryFn: () => api.getReadings(userId),
  staleTime: 5 * 60 * 1000,
  gcTime: 30 * 60 * 1000,
})

// ✅ Mutation
const { mutate } = useMutation({
  mutationFn: (payload) => api.createReading(payload),
  onSuccess: () => queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: ['readings'] }),
  onError: (err) => logger.error('Failed', { error: err })
})

// ✅ MMKV cache (non-sensitive)
const city = storage.getString('last_birth_city')
storage.setString('last_birth_city', 'Beijing')

// ❌ Don't mix useState + useEffect
const [data, setData] = useState(null)
useEffect(() => { api.getReadings().then(setData) }, [])
```

